{
  "stem": "18258.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She spoke French, English, Czech, and of course, German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother's full name was Rosa-- she had no middle name-- Epstein.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And eventually, of course, she became Rosa Schneider.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was with the cavalry, in-- at that time, quite well known cavalry regiment, the dragoons.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The regiment number was three.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were mainly stationed in Krakow, in Poland, at that time part of the monarchy, of course.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he later on told us many times it was probably the best time of his early life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was freed from the restrictions of his Orthodox Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, in the military, that wasn't observed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I know when he came back from service, he was, well-- how do you say-- he was-- what's the word?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Assimilated.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From then on, he kept the High Holidays just to honor his mother who, till her last day, kept to the absolute Orthodox Jewish customs.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when he got married and moved away, we just didn't keep them anymore except the High Holidays.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mother's family-- they were completely assimilated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't keep anything, not even the High Holidays.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they just lived like all the other people, like the assimilated people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were Austrians, actually.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "More Austrians than Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's the way my family-- that's the way I grow up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in my family, except occasionally, when we got in touch with Dad's mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dad's father had died in 1901, so they was long gone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And only occasionally, when we went to visit Grandmother, of course, we had to abide by her customs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we did that to honor her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My earliest memory might be very funny.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was about three years old in kindergarten.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember one thing very vividly.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
